    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Us</h1>
    <div class="p-4">
        <p class="text-justify text-gray-700">Faridpur Engineering College (FEC) stands as a beacon of academic excellence and technical innovation in Bangladesh. Situated in the heart of Faridpur, the college plays a pivotal role in nurturing the next generation of engineers who are equipped to meet the challenges of an ever-evolving technological landscape. Since its establishment in [2010], the college has been steadfast in it's mission to contribute to national development by producing skilled and competent graduates.</p>
