        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Academic Excellence</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-justify">
            Over the years, FEC has undergone significant transformation, expanding its infrastructure and academic facilities. The college campus is equipped with modern lecture halls, fully functional laboratories, a comprehensive library, and advanced computing facilities. These resources ensure that students have access to the tools and technology they need to excel in their studies.
            The academic programs at FEC are affiliated with the Univesity of Dhaka. This affiliation ensures a robust curriculum, rigorous assessment methods, and adherence to the highest academic standards. DU's involvement has been instrumental in shaping FEC as a trusted institution for engineering education.
